title: Ep. 132: Book Club — 'Zoo Station'
description:
The Ringer's Chris Ryan and Andy Greenwald present their long-awaited installment of the Double Down Bookclub, as they review and discuss 'Zoo Station' by David Downing.

Thank you to everyone who participated.
